{"tid":1356664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鏗鏘集]612/721的傷口 --- 開槍做成左永久殘障","createTime":"2019-07-23T14:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T06:46:55.000Z","uid":176918,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9a24834816e7c68de9ad44b538c9039902acece9","tid":1356664,"uid":176918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRcP6wB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRcP6wB.png&h=6f9ee9b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(721)上環1分鐘半懶人包<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/vpf68vgl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fvpf68vgl&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=6312f188\" target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/vpf68vgl</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你睇完覺得<br />\n&quot;屌! 又係禁 亂開槍!!! &quot;<br />\n&quot;預撚左啦 一定係催淚彈 + 開槍嫁啦!!&quot;<br />\n請你反思下 ...<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n佢班黑警目的係話 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">驅散</span></span></strong><br />\n根本唔洗 用到禁最武力<br />\n催淚彈 + 開槍 + 亂用警棍等等既目的<br />\n係 打到你<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: violet;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">永久殘障</span></ins></span></em></strong><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n612 既義士 就已經比呢D所謂既&quot;低殺傷力&quot;<br />\n已經 好可能 永久殘障<br />\n<br />\n楊老師:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUsAhDm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUsAhDm.png&h=b72e97f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n5ssTbE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn5ssTbE.png&h=e2301c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFlorence:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7X56pik.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7X56pik.png&h=72ec786f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPBQQYh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPBQQYh.png&h=bd08e8ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tXaRAp3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtXaRAp3.png&h=91d5dbd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bcMBmlC855Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbcMBmlC855Y&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=89f41261\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bcMBmlC855Y</a><br />\nRTHK 香港電台<br />\n發佈日期：2019年7月22日<br />\n反逃犯法例引發連串風波，6月12日警方施放150枚催淚彈，20發布袋彈，及未有公布實際數字的橡膠子彈，所用的裝備，遠超過2014年的佔中運動87枚催淚彈。612當日有不少片段顯示，警方近距離向示威者採用武器。<br />\n<br />\n外界<br />\n關注，政府是否用了不合乎比例的武器；是否採用過度武力。政府官員一致口徑表示，示威者可以向監警會投訴。<br />\n<br />\n不過，612中遭警方過度使用武力對待的傷者，對監警會有戒心，擔心投訴資料會成為警方控告他們的罪證。公眾亦要求一個獨立調查委員會，徹底調查事件前因後果，對示威參加者及警方才公道。<br />\n<br />\n7月的抗議活動中，警民衝突越來越激烈，監警會主席梁定邦表示會主動檢視6月9日至7月2日的衝突場面成因，及建議如何預防類似事件發生，並會將報告給特首及警務處長。但監警會有限制，未必符合公眾期望。<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"be1a2e916ce12f7ac583afdc3e1a12b8a4eacd4b","tid":1356664,"uid":165246,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:24:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">１。全面撤回送中<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗暴動</span></span>"},{"pid":"367416b4205acce485a87853d118ada2d2ef67a6","tid":1356664,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a81973c2f4ca7d7d48e681a2d91b03d5a9d92a32","tid":1356664,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:25:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"506b476965400c7f02f090e5f9d262669468b932","tid":1356664,"uid":79916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:26:14.000Z","msg":"推 仲有721!!"},{"pid":"12d3fa4fa976c430210cd3164f39d5f064d29928","tid":1356664,"uid":67177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:27:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd30d1bbdbf9bd8e3226ef0332ad977466247f3f","tid":1356664,"uid":72801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b0c1f7801391063f59d8464fde10774ea273dc","tid":1356664,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌 好撚嬲 推 牛屎佬打人都無插人眼呀 大家記住</span></span>"},{"pid":"15d701c446b9ba3019ad352639e53da89177456f","tid":1356664,"uid":283971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:27:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"821cb3a3830d9d262dc68089e4ac12d5997742f8","tid":1356664,"uid":237077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nBtCFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nBtCFX.jpg&h=a3d5aa01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"143f2c1e16f129e920c85c40e382a38ecbdf0b92","tid":1356664,"uid":276003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:28:25.000Z","msg":"不合理武力使用!!! <br />\n對真武力人仕既黑幫, 黑警就龜縮"},{"pid":"1542fbd440959aadf79c57bd0af7a55a2a44835e","tid":1356664,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"<code>（瞄準政權）上環黑警36槍企圖殺害抗爭者 中共策劃元朗恐襲</code><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">所有嘢都係中共係背後策劃<br />\n如果呢個政權係仆街係十惡不赦<br />\n咁擁護佢嘅黑警 黑社會都一樣咁仆街<br />\n咁十惡不赦 但唔好浪費咁多時間係呢<br />\n班卒仔到 <br />\n主力打大佬 瞄準返中共 唔好out focus唔係就真係對唔住咁多位被呢個政權殺害嘅戰友</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">義士宣言：不排除成立臨時立法會</div></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350879</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>支持前線所有決定</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n民情，輿論，選票，呢啲唔洗我哋去諗，點去收拾所謂嘅殘局，就交比啲政治人物去煩啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋要做嘅係我哋認為啱嘅事</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4LYjFvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4LYjFvR.jpg&h=d444c005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<code>「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）</code><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">五大訴求，勿忘初衷\n遍地開花，不撤不散\n打倒軍權，反對國家恐怖主義\n光復香港，時代革命</code></pre><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n定性721黑警上環血腥鎮壓，元朗黑社會恐怖襲擊，警黑合作散播中國國家恐怖主義:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察戰線:</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gq6kYx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gq6kYx.jpg&h=1f5648e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hY7P3bT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhY7P3bT.jpg&h=5c1777d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察冇預警下開槍射36發橡膠彈，有人爆頭，警察已無視通例，已失去合法性<br />\n警察放任黑社會打市民，完全冇制止，並假指無發現武器收隊，傳媒發現雙方實有公開溝通<br />\n警察公然無視電話求助，元朗警署落閘，違反警隊職責<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑社會戰線:</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7DWJcw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7DWJcw.jpg&h=92c6a934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idEKR5S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidEKR5S.jpg&h=e6380dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拉攏任何政治冷感市民，有錢人，元朗問題非個別事件，收錢恐襲任何區都會發生，任何人都有機會中招<br />\n俾藍絲睇到佢地支持何君堯即係支持黑社會打人斬人，令藍絲同何君堯反面<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際戰線:</span><br />\n向外國抗議中國政府散播國家恐怖主義<br />\n向外媒及各國投訴香港警察包庇黑社會合作各自無差別打人，違反通例無預警開槍，已失去合法性<br />\n港鐵作為國際地鐵聯盟之一公然妄顧市民安危強逼市民離開車廂被打<br />\n黑社會涉嫌在元朗發動恐襲襲擊，主腦直指中共政府<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自發治安戰線:</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sf52DMn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsf52DMn.jpg&h=ecc7650f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OejSgx3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOejSgx3.jpg&h=01748b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港防衛隊  正式成立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1342844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1342844</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【HKSDF】香港自衛隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352390</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[請長期置頂] 民間保衛隊初形 公民團結行公義 任何抗命運動適用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351343</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【元朗恐襲】真心，如果眾籌，成立「香港自衛隊保安公司」優先過登報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1346745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1346745</a><br />\n</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港鐵戰線:</span><br />\n全面係所有車站招貼: 元朗站逼市民落車被打，妄顧安危<br />\n一定要令每個站每個角落都見到<br />\n全面不合作運動，再加宣傳市民全面罷坐港鐵<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>唔好再比政府帶風向啦，元朗恐襲完個個第二日正正常常返工有冇搞錯呀，仲要出面一個行動post都冇！由今日起要令交通癱瘓，救救香港唔該</code><br />\n<br />\n[突發] 有痴線佬係地鐵裸跑導致延誤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351224\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351224</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n經過今日我發現左幾個問題：<br />\n1.我地既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標係要停哂成架列車，唔係拖延架車</span></span>，目標係要停列<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>推到上報</strong></span></span>，咁打工仔先可以大條道理咁講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇車返唔到工</span></span>，報都推唔到既話只會令大家覺得令到佢地遲到，到時會開始屌返我地轉頭，所以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到時候亦都需要做文宣係咁airdrop</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 人手太散太易比人捉，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中返係幾個點</span></span>就好了，唔係既話好容易比人屌走，唔好再攞阻到幾次門打飛機<br />\n<br />\n2. 香港人真係太多包袱太驚返唔到工比人屌，直接令到響應人數唔夠而呢場運動未有很成功。但係我想講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">返唔到工大家都有份，想返唔到工就要大家一齊做，唔好等人幫你做</span></span>。當每個人都一齊響應令交通癱瘓既時候就唔會有返工遲到既出現，係返唔到工。<br />\n<br />\n3. 太多人去到之後怕左就暈唔到，點都要有一個人開始架啦，香港人就係咁，乜都好驚，所以你有啲膽既話不妨第一個唔舒服。就好似今日大圍咁令大家都重點果種火。<br />\n<br />\n頂門呢啲真係唔好做啦，因為頂門頂唔到幾多次，都阻唔到好耐。<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔小心跌左野入<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔小心跌咗嘢入路軌</span></span>，跌左火機果啲就唔好啦，不過跌左一定要同職員講，唔係好危險<br />\n<br />\n2. 見到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有人唔舒服要拉緊急制停車</span></span>，冇計人命關天，一卡有五隻，拉哂佢，拉埋格離果卡都仲得，唔洗同佢客氣<br />\n<br />\n3. 唔小心<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">整壞架車是但一道門</span></span>，就成架車都唔用得，情況就好似琴日九龍塘咁，成條線delay十幾分鐘<br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">經過恐襲大家變哂痴線佬落哂路軌</span></span>，跑又好叫又好<br />\n<br />\n大家都係係地鐵唔舒服姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n三罷交癱tg link</strong></span></span>:<br />\n<br />\n大group:<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/mtr723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmtr723&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=1418ff10\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/mtr723</a><br />\n<br />\n荃灣綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1HDsPqChixQv4i2Yw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhP1HDsPqChixQv4i2Yw&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=1cfb62dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1HDsPqChixQv4i2Yw</a><br />\n<br />\n觀塘綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1AfZbR7xvsS0C6h4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhP1AfZbR7xvsS0C6h4A&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=76c42a78\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1AfZbR7xvsS0C6h4A</a><br />\n<br />\n港島綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP0jHZcU9BYIAXhEFWw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhP0jHZcU9BYIAXhEFWw&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=a5b1c9ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP0jHZcU9BYIAXhEFWw</a><br />\n<br />\n東鐵綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1iH0REZYKW6RDSItw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhP1iH0REZYKW6RDSItw&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=19bc72d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1iH0REZYKW6RDSItw</a><br />\n<br />\n西鐵綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1GjqX7E0kHgLmf8xw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhP1GjqX7E0kHgLmf8xw&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=44df950d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1GjqX7E0kHgLmf8xw</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其他紀律部隊戰線:</span><br />\n拉攏非警察的紀律部隊，要求表態，為違反紀律部隊職責的警察投訴<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721宣言</span></span><br />\n<br />\n    <br />\n    <a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=1d1e5ae9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a><br />\n    <br />\n<br />\n條片只有<span style=\"color: green;\">3000views</span> <br />\n但留言勁多5毛 某程度證明有用<br />\n（排序較新至舊 你會發現多得過份）<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手留言 引啲5毛一齊推上<span style=\"color: maroon;\">Youtube熱門</span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">歡迎轉發及引用推Post</code></pre></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ac43fe670dead3fe5f2dd1388466a94b08853f0d","tid":1356664,"uid":176918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:30:20.000Z","msg":"推到大家再一次醒覺"},{"pid":"b41a0d924fb24f2d31126e465a971ae475da5ae8","tid":1356664,"uid":25440,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"94b0c1f7801391063f59d8464fde10774ea273dc","tid":1356664,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌 好撚嬲 推 牛屎佬打人都無插人眼呀 大家記住</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:30:29.000Z","msg":"兩幫都pk <br />\n唔好幫任何一邊洗白<br />\n兩幫都係暴徒！"},{"pid":"e4753682b7d45823a475ff0c4920cc08b2e811dd","tid":1356664,"uid":76558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:31:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 一定要追究黑警濫權濫用暴力 <br />\n造成永久性傷害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警死全家！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e1e7991a27f12ea66fffc946fe4fd6a51651ffe8","tid":1356664,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c491a5131f928d1d9e9e4581dec57362b3e8b2","tid":1356664,"uid":176918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"楊老師 0.3<br />\n係指 做完手術都只可以回復到正常視力既0.3<br />\n姐係冇可能完全回復正常"},{"pid":"791f7407a4199f3